{"tid":894964,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人d老豆老母好撚痴線 好撚廢","createTime":"2018-11-08T19:42:27.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-13T10:20:30.000Z","uid":10679,"like":20,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"e036f21acd4248290f4615692fbbb5b21df2265b","tid":894964,"uid":10679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-08T19:42:27.000Z","msg":"盲目孝順撚可以出返去，唔歡迎你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n老母：<br />\n1. 燙衫燙到著火，好彩我係屋企，如果唔係就燒左間屋<br />\n2. 好鍾意將d用完嘅洗手液／沖涼液加勁多水溝稀（用埋痴係個樽身果d），如果你唔知佢溝稀左而你一手㩒落去，就彈到周圍都係（包括自己），而且係起唔到泡洗唔到手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n3. d 水煲 煎pan用左十年八載，甩哂coating都唔肯換；試過見到雪櫃支蠔油過左期幾年，你掉佢d野就屌鳩你<br />\n4. 廚房抹完野果張抹手紙唔會掉，話未用哂張紙，留返下次再用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n老豆：<br />\n1. 儲儲埋埋d舊報紙唔知做乜鳩，你掉佢d野就屌鳩你<br />\n2. 好鍾意係牆到鑽窿，鑽完一係搵d綠色嘅塞 塞住佢，之後又冇整任何野係上面；一係就搵d唔知咩物料抆落去封返住佢，隔一排果pat「膠」會變到灰灰黑黑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n3. 無啦啦換左你道房門，新門係鎖唔到，而且當你掩埋佢果陣，有少少風就吹得開，要勁大力嘭埋道門先閂到<br />\n4. 死都要搵個膠盒「CUP」住風筒個尾，話會冇咁易壞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n5. 正常屋企有一個門鎖，鐵閘再有一個鎖。但係我屋企有兩個門鎖，三個鐵閘鎖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 果兩個門鎖扭嘅方向係唔一樣，係相反。果三個鐵閘鎖，一個係鎖匙，兩個係要加鎖頭果d，但係永遠都唔會加個鎖頭落去，唔知佢焊嚟做乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">重點係佢地d雜物搞到好多甲由呀屌！！！</span></span><br />\n永遠有需要嘅野都唔會做，甲由又唔理，d牆紙用左幾廿年發哂霉，一潮濕吽哂蟲仔又唔理<br />\n唉屌你老母 唔好講咩做咩唔搬出去住，有能力一早搬左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f53c11c4a5f0ba83ab8d5a8f4f540c7ddcb7bbb","tid":894964,"uid":78336,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-08T19:43:57.000Z","msg":"諗住入黎話我老母成個星期d碗碟都唔洗<br />\n睇黎我可以出翻去"},{"pid":"53318e8c0420aa2501da107285c5cd2ce6db85c9","tid":894964,"uid":201604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-08T19:44:00.000Z","msg":"好好笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f79ef19deb439679350047a964b1e6373a08d8e6","tid":894964,"uid":113085,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-08T19:50:27.000Z","msg":"老母同你差唔多，仲加多樣係儲物狂。<br />\n佢地係有精神病，唔係廢。<br />\n呢啲強迫症睇精神科都無用。"},{"pid":"3a79e8c76ba39354b6e8e5c24a20962fb6cd9601","tid":894964,"uid":195975,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8f53c11c4a5f0ba83ab8d5a8f4f540c7ddcb7bbb","tid":894964,"uid":78336,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-08T19:43:57.000Z","msg":"諗住入黎話我老母成個星期d碗碟都唔洗<br />\n睇黎我可以出翻去"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-08T19:57:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e209d8f6ab479b7c71b4b8cdb16aa67f807ecfd3","tid":894964,"uid":7790,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"f79ef19deb439679350047a964b1e6373a08d8e6","tid":894964,"uid":113085,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-08T19:50:27.000Z","msg":"老母同你差唔多，仲加多樣係儲物狂。<br />\n佢地係有精神病，唔係廢。<br />\n呢啲強迫症睇精神科都無用。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-08T20:00:12.000Z","msg":"我老母都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n儲埋d死人膠袋、用完既膠樽玻璃樽話拎去回收，<br />\n次次都放到無哂位都唔拎走，我次次都幫佢掉撚哂<br />\n係咪個個老母都係儲物狂"},{"pid":"b9b631a99d2c88ecdbbb0a0a1f968f51f15909fc","tid":894964,"uid":66436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-08T20:01:56.000Z","msg":"真係想見識下堆鎖"},{"pid":"6df6c18cea0fbcd06ed1c1d8cc65d1da8da837de"